## FreeRTOS Tasks

### Medical Task
Reads Heart Rate, SpO₂, and Body Temperature.

### Facility Task
Reads Room Temperature, Oxygen Level, and AQI.

### Display Task
Alternates between Medical Dashboard and Facility Dashboard on the OLED.

### MQTT Simulation Task
Publishes simulated MQTT topics through the Serial Monitor.

### Alert Task
Triggers LED and buzzer during abnormal conditions.

### Summary Task
Calculates and displays average sensor values periodically.

---

## Simulated MQTT Topics

Medical Dashboard

```
medical/patient
```

Facility Dashboard

```
facility/environment
```

Alert Topic

```
alerts/critical
```

Summary Topic

```
medical/summary
```

---

## Alert Conditions

- SpO₂ < 92%
- Body Temperature > 38°C
- AQI > 150

When any condition is detected:

- LED blinks
- Buzzer activates
- Alert message is printed on the Serial Monitor

